Screens
  # Signup
  One email input which sends a confirmation token if user is not already present
  If user is already present, user resends a message with one of the reminders


Send a confirmation message when user signs up
Send an item in sequence to the user every day at 12 midnight UTC
  this email also has a link which allows the user to manage their list items

User can send an email to 'inbox+uniqueuserid@simplereminder.com'
  and this will add this item to their list
